title: S12 Ep166: Strange Creatures & Curses
itunes:title: Strange Creatures & Curses
description:
Maria D'Andrea discusses her connection to the spirit world and the mystical monsters of its realms; The Djinn, Aliens & Interdimensional Beings.

Can these creatures be sent to us as Curses? How do we protect ourselves and should we summon these magickal monsters to aide us?
